{"tid":1168914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發展局：香園圍公路助完善大灣區一小時生活圈","createTime":"2019-05-24T04:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T05:02:20.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba77c90b118d8e7bbc6f2e35b986fc62173af90","tid":1168914,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190524_20190524-121702.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190524_20190524-121702.jpg&h=a8088636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連接蓮塘/香園圍口岸的香園圍公路，將於星期日早上8時正式通車，今日舉行通車儀式。<br />\n<br />\n發展局常任秘書長林世雄致辭時表示，新公路啟用後，能有效改善北區及沙頭角公路的交通負荷，同時可分流文錦渡及沙頭角邊境管制站的過境交通，再配合連接深圳蓮塘口岸的深圳東部過境高速公路直達龍崗，經惠鹽或深汕高速公路通往粵東，為香港及深圳東、惠州及粵東間，提供有效率的跨境通道，進一步完善粵港澳大灣區一小時生活圈的佈局。"},{"pid":"3fe7ff50a15e295475b9ff99de94dc371c9bade8","tid":1168914,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1106866&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1106866%26csid%3D261_341&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=396400e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1106866&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"7382f3939a75a36c51c3b6613cce0c9d32597505","tid":1168914,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"條公路通車又點，個口岸呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8187cb5bc5525370ca576570e2cf6ef84c1ab8c4","tid":1168914,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb5d1e9980aa0d279bdb9563ab00fa012058a06","tid":1168914,"uid":103230,"like":